    "author_association": "COLLABORATOR",
    "body": "Keep in mind that the use of a \"workspace\" specific settings file only overrides \"user\" specific settings for that workspace.  And that is typically what you want.  That is, a user might prefer tabs to spaces but this project uses spaces.  So adding that setting to an editor config file will ensure that spaces are used for this user in only this workspace.  In his own projects, tabs will still be used.",
